room_title: Escape room "Clue-Dunnit?" by Escape Reality Games in Sarasota

room_description: World famous mystery novelist Una Owen has just been found dead in her family's cabin.  The police think it was a suicide, but her assistant Grace thinks something nefarious happened out there in the woods...  It's up to your team of private detectives to find the truth.
